[02:45] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this. We have the unit slipped inside of these grooves here, so it\'s not going to go anywhere. And then, we have these anti-tip'

[02:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'sliding brackets. So, for whatever reason, if this tries to move, it\'s going to hit this first. So, we have that locked in. So, it\'ll hit this before anything happens. So, you put your foam in before that.'

[03:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'We just cut that real easy, so everything is nice and sealed. And now, we have this gray adhesive that goes all the way along the top side after we did all of that. So, now, when we slide our window, check this out.'

